" Bubble lines
map <C-Up> [e
map <C-Down> ]e
vmap <C-Up> [egv
vmap <C-Down> ]egv

" Indentation
map <Leader><[> <<
map <Leader><]> >>
vmap <Leader><]> >gv
vmap <Leader><[> <gv

" Commenting
map <Leader></> <plug>NERDCommenterToggle<CR>
vmap <Leader></> <plug>NERDCommenterToggle<CR>

" Viewports
map <Leader><Up> <C-w>k
map <Leader><Down> <C-w>j
map <Leader><Right> <C-w>l
map <Leader><Left> <C-w>h
